OL,3,C'Brutal, savage, frenzied': Sister
OL,4,Csays murderer was 'inhuman'
OL,6,FThe sister of a woman who was murdered
OL,7,Fby an asylum seeker in Wolverhampton
OL,8,Fhas spoken about the 'life sentence'
OL,9,Fof 'pain and suffering' she and her
OL,10,Ffamily must now live with.
OL,12,FDeng Chol Majek has been sentenced to
OL,13,Flife with a minimum term of 29 years
OL,14,Fafter being found guilty of murdering
OL,15,FRhiannon Whyte, 27, on a train station
OL,16,Fplatform on 20 October 2024.
OL,18,FDuring the sentencing hearing, the
OL,19,Fcourt heart about the impact Ms
OL,20,FWhyte's death had on her sister
OL,21,FAlexandra Whyte.
