OL,3,C'Brutal, savage, frenzied': Sister
OL,4,Csays murderer was 'inhuman'
OL,6,FIn a statement, she spoke about how
OL,7,Fthe "vicious and pitiless assault on a
OL,8,Fterrified and defenceless young woman"
OL,9,Fis something she has had "to address
OL,10,Fevery day".
OL,12,FShe also said Majek's not guilty plea
OL,13,Fadded "insult to injury" and meant
OL,14,Fthat she and her family "had to sit
OL,15,Fand endure reliving Rhiannon's last
OL,16,Fmoments over and over again" in the
OL,17,F"very public setting" of the murder
OL,18,Ftrial.
