OL,3,C'Brutal, savage, frenzied': Sister
OL,4,Csays murderer was 'inhuman'
OL,6,FAlexandra described her sister as
OL,7,F"smart, kind, funny, thoughtful,
OL,8,Fcaring, and hardworking."
OL,10,FShe added: "Most importantly she
OL,11,Fbelonged to us. A mother, daughter,
OL,12,Fsister, aunty, niece, cousin,
OL,13,Fgranddaughter, and friend to so many.
OL,15,F"Being alive to this only makes it
OL,16,Fharder to comprehend and accept that
OL,17,Fher bright future has been stolen from
OL,18,Fher and all of us so brutally.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
