OL,3,C'Brutal, savage, frenzied': Sister
OL,4,Csays murderer was 'inhuman'
OL,6,F"She faced challenges with courage and
OL,7,Fgrace, never letting anything diminish
OL,8,Fher spirit.
OL,10,F"Her resilience taught us the
OL,11,Fimportance of staying strong in the
OL,12,Fface of adversity and always remaining
OL,13,Funited through love and determination.
OL,15,F"She died surrounded by family and
OL,16,Ffriends and we held her in our arms
OL,17,Ffor three days until she succumbed to
OL,18,Fher injuries."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
