OL,3,C'Brutal, savage, frenzied': Sister
OL,4,Csays murderer was 'inhuman'
OL,6,FAddressing Majek directly, she said:
OL,7,F"Rhiannon showed so much more courage
OL,8,Fthan you. You continue to show no
OL,9,Fremorse and to take no responsibility
OL,10,Ffor your cowardly actions.
OL,12,F"We still don't know or understand why
OL,13,Fyou stalked, hunted and preyed upon
OL,14,FRhiannon. Cornering her before
OL,15,Funleashing your vicious and unprovoked
OL,16,Fattack.
OL,18,F"Throughout this agonising court
OL,19,Fprocess, you have given us nothing.
OL,20,FWhy her? What had she done to you to
OL,21,Fdeserve this callous treatment?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
