OL,3,C'Brutal, savage, frenzied': Sister
OL,4,Csays murderer was 'inhuman'
OL,6,F"As if it was not hard enough to lose
OL,7,FRhiannon, we have had to endure a year
OL,8,Fand three months of heartache and
OL,9,Fpain, unable to grieve because of our
OL,10,Ffight for justice.
OL,12,F"You took advantage of our judicial
OL,13,Fsystem with your blatant ignorance and
OL,14,Farrogance, subjecting my family to
OL,15,Fpainfully detailed witness statements
OL,16,Fwhich reduced Rhiannon to being spoken
OL,17,Fabout as evidence rather than the
OL,19,Fbeautiful human she was.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
