OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F377A1769810976
OL,3,C'Brutal, savage, frenzied': Sister
OL,4,Csays murderer was 'inhuman'
OL,6,F"We were unable to give her a funeral
OL,7,Ffor four months because she was still
OL,8,F'evidence!' Rhiannon was dehumanised
OL,9,Fat every turn throughout this process.
OL,10,FBy you and your cowardly defence.
OL,12,F"We now know from the evidence we had
OL,13,Fto listen to that she was brave. She
OL,14,Ffought for her life under a brutal,
OL,15,Fsavage and frenzied attack from
OL,16,Fsomeone we see as inhuman, more like
OL,17,Fan animal."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
