OL,3,C'Brutal, savage, frenzied': Sister
OL,4,Csays murderer was 'inhuman'
OL,6,FAlexandra also spoke about having the
OL,7,Fresponsibility of raising Rhiannon's
OL,8,Fson: "I struggled to find the words to
OL,9,Fconvey that this wasn't done by the
OL,10,Fsort of monster he might have seen on
OL,11,FTV or read about in a book but by a
OL,12,Freal person.
OL,14,F"You will always however be the
OL,15,Fmonster who stole his mother."
OL,17,FFinally she told Majek how Rhiannon's
OL,18,Ffamily "wish to see you spend the rest
OL,19,Fof your life alone and devoid of the
OL,20,Flove and warmth of the support of
OL,21,Ffamily and friends.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
